# Mock & Missing Connections Audit Results

## Executive Summary
The system currently defaults to **Mock** providers for nearly all external data (Calendar, Prices, Quotes, Proxies). This is a **P0 PROD BLOCKER** because it bypasses safety gates (news windows, price deviation) and decision-quality checks (market proxies). Additionally, several internal logic bridges (Risk evaluation subscription, Lot sizing) are unimplemented.

